<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f4f8; color: #1a202c; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #1a56db 100%); padding: 40px 48px; text-align: center; }
    .header-logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .body { padding: 48px; }
    .success-icon { font-size: 64px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a202c; margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; }
    .text { font-size: 15px; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .cta-btn { display: block; width: fit-content; margin: 24px auto; padding: 14px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a56db 0%, #7c3aed 100%); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; }
    .warning { background: #fffbeb; border-left: 4px solid #f6ad55; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 24px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 48px; background: #f7fafc; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-logo">⚖️ {{appName}}</div>
      <div class="header-sub">Account Security</div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
      <p class="greeting">Password Changed Successfully</p>
      <p class="text">
        Hi <strong>{{firstName}}</strong>, your <strong>{{appName}}</strong> account password has been 
        successfully changed. You can now log in with your new password.
      </p>
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/login" class="cta-btn">Log In Now →</a>
      <div class="warning">
        ⚠️ If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately 
        and secure your account.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
